text: I really like the piece.  it sounded very close to the theme.  It had a good over all feel.  I would think is was a little on the short side.  Since in most cases you listen to a dungeon theme/song for a long time; having it longer allows for it to have a little more depth and growing harmonies.  Another point to consider for these types is that when looped the player/listener won't hear looping so much and won't get as tired of hearing it for a prolonged time.
